The paper deals with image recognition and image processing, which are both subfields of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves optimizing for machine interpretability, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve evaluating the method on different recognition tasks, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or information retrieval (cs.IR).
